### Invoice API Requests

### Create a new invoice
POST {{host}}/api/invoices
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operationId": "OP-12345",
  "amount": 150.00
}

### Get invoice by ID
GET {{host}}/api/invoices/INV-12345

### Get all invoices for a specific operation
GET {{host}}/api/invoices/operation/OP-12345

### Update invoice status
POST {{host}}/api/invoices/INV-12345/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "PAID"
}

### Example with other status values
# Status can be: PENDING, PAID, CANCELLED
POST http://localhost:8080/api/invoices/INV-12345/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "CANCELLED"
}
